<p>Increases zero page pointer address in [ parameter 1 ] with [ parameter 2] bytes.  
<code>
	// zp is a pointer.
	// Point to bank 0 screen
	  zp := $0400;
	  for j:=0 to 25 do begin
	  	for i:=0 to 40 do begin
	  		// Fill the screen with some random value i
	  		zp[i]:=i;
	  	end;
	  	// increase the pointer with 40 (1 row )
	  	inczp(zp, 40);
	  end;
</code>